      • hasUniqueInstance

        public boolean hasUniqueInstance()
        If this type should refer to a IConfigurable with a unique instance. If this is true, the IConfigurable should have a public static void initInstance(ExtendedConfig eConfig) method and also a public static (? extends IConfigurable) getInstance() method.
        Returns:
        If it has a unique instance.
